                "Finding a balance between dishes inspired by authentic recipes and creating a modern take on
                classic cuisine sees a loyal following of Canberra locals returning for a mouth-watering feast."
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="website" style="margin-bottom:100px"><a href="http://www.jewelofindia.com.au/">WEBSITE</a></div>
